message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance, my name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Finally! I've been waiting for ages to speak with someone. My claim hasn't been processed yet, and it's been weeks!
I'm really sorry to hear about the delay in processing your claim. I understand your frustration. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for completing security, John. Can you also provide me with your date of birth?
Great, thank you for that. Just one more piece of information for security. Can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
That's all correct, thank you. Now, how can I assist you with your claim? Can you please provide me with some more details?
I've already explained everything to your company multiple times. Can't you see it on your system?
I apologize for any inconvenience, John. I understand your frustration. Let me check the system for any updates. Please allow me a moment.
It's been too long already. I need this sorted out immediately.
I completely understand, John. I value your feedback, and we'll do our best to find a way forward. I appreciate your patience during this process.
I'm glad that I was able to help, John. I've escalated your case, and we'll prioritize it for you. We'll reach a resolution as soon as possible. Is there anything else you'd like to address today?
No, that's all for now. Just make sure it's done this time.
Thank you for contacting us, John. We appreciate your patience and we're here to help. Have a great day!
